<title>UK: UK's First Leisure pays 46 mln stg for gyms.</title>
<headline>UK's First Leisure pays 46 mln stg for gyms.</headline>
<dateline>LONDON 1997-05-30</dateline>
<text>
<p>Britain's First Leisure Corporation Plc said on Friday it had bought the Riverside group of health and fitness clubs for an initial 46 million stg.</p>
<p>First Leisure said it had also repaid Riverside's borrowings of 12 million stg. It said an additional two million stg was payable dependent on Riverside securing an interest in a further development in London.</p>
